    dc:description "Fig. 31. Laboulbenia spp. A. L. eubradycelli Huldén. Mature thallus showing elevations on ventral margin of perithecium (arrows). – B–F. L. fasciculata Peyr. B, E. Mature thalli. C–D. Immature thalli with labelled insertion cell (ic). F. Mature thallus on Chlaenius from Spain. Scale bars: 50 µm. Photographs from slides ZMUC C-F-122533 (A), ZMUC C-F-124273 (B), ZMUC C-F-123598 (C), ZMUC C-F- 122639 (D–E), BCB-XE56 (F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5829020/files/figure.png" ;
